{"tid":1968844,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲開始種票","createTime":"2020-04-12T03:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T06:49:43.000Z","uid":27141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be89653ee5869ee2c4d30c64012376efb94e79e0","tid":1968844,"uid":27141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次開post<br />\n<br />\n話說我呀媽尋日係牛池灣見到有人派口罩等等嘅防疫物資<br />\n望咗望佢地要18歲以上先派<br />\n仲要登記身份證先可以拎<br />\n而佢唔同黃議員咁只寫頭三個數字<br />\n係成組抄哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地就話自己係廣西同鄉會<br />\n<br />\n有個中年婦人就叫大家唔好亂俾身份證人<br />\n等陣拎去借錢都得啦<br />\n班搞手即刻話唔好信個婦人，佢係黃絲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後留低嘅得班公公婆婆<br />\n大家一定要同屋企人講口罩呢啲派就派<br />\n唔洗寫咩身份證<br />\n如果屋企人係藍絲<br />\n唔洗講咩種唔種票<br />\n話拎嚟借錢就會即刻知驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b384e02d8092d5b12fb41730090ee2afa62fa0","tid":1968844,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deceffe85fbb0ca11514f9a05c8d7e17dd5a2160","tid":1968844,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"開始咗好多年啦,新野係開七人工會同香港爭選委票同奴工界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166c278ad9ad9bad952eb2b244712fd4157a8abc","tid":1968844,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"我一早幫住係老人院嘅家人取消選民資格。<br />\n<br />\n幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c893f1595a9ab8f65c28bdede90eaf85afccffc6","tid":1968844,"uid":57413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24114523834513ac802e